{"tid":2454994,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"糗！巴黎宣布破獲市值3400萬毒品 結果全是哈瑞寶糖果","createTime":"2021-03-20T16:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T17:17:28.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02b9d46b3d60bd1e1288723da9613f950615e26e","tid":2454994,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎警方本周宣布破獲市價超過100萬歐元（約新台幣3393萬元）的毒品案，<br />\n <br />\n未料最終發現那批毒品其實是糖果。<br />\n <br />\n巴黎警方17日公布被磨成粉紅色粉末的毒品照片，稱這些毒品為搖頭丸。然而，了解案情<br />\n <br />\n的消息人士透露，粉末後來被發現是磨碎的糖果。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n    法新社報導，更確切地說，這是知名糖果品牌哈瑞寶（Haribo）所生產Tagada草莓糖，<br />\n <br />\n目前尚不清楚為何當時警方會將糖果粉末當成毒品，而糖果被磨成粉末的原因也有待釐清。<br />\n <br />\n然而搞了烏龍，但巴黎警方仍拘留一名嫌犯，因為警方在現場發現了失竊的手機以及可製<br />\n <br />\n造搖頭丸的機器。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n    泰國警方去年宣稱破獲最大宗的K他命毒品案，結果送到實驗室化驗後才發現是清潔劑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/20/realtime/11909516.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2Frealtime%2F11909516.png&h=04b5f337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/03/20/realtime/11909517.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F03%2F20%2Frealtime%2F11909517.png&h=c81ff3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5331141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5331141&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=2e1b57fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5331141</a>"},{"pid":"9325eaf66c5b81bc0ce0f40ba617a9e007fe004b","tid":2454994,"uid":190789,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"全世界啲黑警都食屎屙飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b6e96cc4722b72b9c62d5414f1c9d27d2c1168","tid":2454994,"uid":1284,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T16:49:34.